      <div class="section-tag">About Me Snapshot</div>
      <h2>Hi, I’m Ella Joy B. Ignacio</h2>
      <p>I’m a 24-year-old content operations and social media support specialist based in BGC, Philippines. I graduated with a Bachelor of Science in Business Administration major in Management, and I’ve built experience across YouTube operations, social media management, website support, admin work, customer service, and digital marketing.</p>
      <p>I work behind the scenes to help creators, founders, and businesses stay consistent online — from creating Shorts and thumbnails to managing content calendars, uploading blogs, supporting email campaigns, and organizing daily workflows.</p>
      
      <div class="snapshot-grid">
        <div class="snapshot-card">
          <div class="snapshot-card-title">Location</div>
          <div class="snapshot-card-val">BGC, Philippines</div>
        </div>
        <div class="snapshot-card">
          <div class="snapshot-card-title">Education</div>
          <div class="snapshot-card-val">BSBA Major in Management</div>
        </div>
        <div class="snapshot-card">
          <div class="snapshot-card-title">Core Channel Support</div>
          <div class="snapshot-card-val">YouTube & Social Media Support</div>
        </div>
        <div class="snapshot-card">
          <div class="snapshot-card-title">Digital Admin</div>
          <div class="snapshot-card-val">Website Management</div>
        </div>
        <div class="snapshot-card">
          <div class="snapshot-card-title">Corporate Track</div>
          <div class="snapshot-card-val">Admin & CSR Experience</div>
